{
  "stem": "11641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you worked-- you know, you work weeks over there, and then change of some-- to some-- to some place else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were building part of a factory itself, adjacent to the factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were building.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were fed a little bit better-- not that much better, but fed better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the-- the fear of death was not there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, that's-- this was the main thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whereby in-- in Plaszow, you're not aware-- you're not sure will you come back alive, because of this-- of Get.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But by-- by Schindler, you-- you were not-- the fear of death was not there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not that you had more food or you had other things, but the fear was not there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was the main thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were in barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole thing was in the barracks done.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to have somebody you know in the barracks in order to talk to him, to do anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- some we have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where I belong now to [NON-ENGLISH] Society, you know, I belong to the New French Krakow Society, where mostly, a lot of them who were by Schindler belonged there, and a few of them that I was with them in-- in a [NON-ENGLISH] by Schindler-- a few of them.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some I don't remember, and some do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It all depends upon the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had nothing to-- he was-- he only talked to the higher echelon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- [LAUGHS] --19 maybe at that time or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was passing by.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't ask me exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He asked our foreman, look, how are you doing here, and all the other things, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, he-- you know, like anybody-- human being is asking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Brunnlitz, we didn't go directly.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
